\c 39
\s Ukunqotshwa kweJerusalema
\p
\v 1 Ngomnyaka wesificamunwemunye kaZedekhiya inkosi yakoJuda,\x + 39.1,2; 52.4-7. 2 Kho. 25.1-4.\x* ngenyanga yetshumi, kwafika uNebhukadirezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni lebutho lakhe lonke, bamelana leJerusalema, bayivimbezela.
\v 2 Ngomnyaka wetshumi lanye kaZedekhiya, ngenyanga yesine, ngolwesificamunwemunye lwenyanga, umuzi wafohlelwa.
\v 3 Zonke iziphathamandla zenkosi yeBhabhiloni zasezingena,\x + 38.17,18,22.\x* zahlala esangweni eliphakathi,\x + 1.15.\x* oNerigali-Sharezi, uSamiganebo, uSarisekimi, uRabisarisi,\x + 39.13. Dan. 1.3. 2 Kho. 18.17.\x* uNerigali-Sharezi, uRabimagi,\x + 39.13. Mat. 2.1.\x* lazo zonke ezinye iziphathamandla zenkosi yeBhabhiloni.
\p
\v 4 Kwasekusithi lapho uZedekhiya inkosi yakoJuda\x + 39.10; 52.7-16. 2 Kho. 25.4-12.\x* lawo wonke amadoda empi bezibona, babaleka, baphuma emzini ebusuku \add nge\add*ndlela yesivande senkosi, ngesango eliphakathi kwemiduli emibili; waphuma \add nge\add*ndlela yamagceke.
\v 5 Kodwa ibutho lamaKhaladiya laxotshana labo, lamfica uZedekhiya emagcekeni eJeriko; selimbambile lamenyusela kuNebhukadinezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni eRibila, elizweni leHamathi,\x + 2 Kho. 23.33.\x* owakhuluma izigwebo ezimelene laye.\x + Hez. 17.15.\x*
\v 6 Inkosi yeBhabhiloni yasibulala amadodana kaZedekhiya eRibila emehlweni akhe;\x + 38.23.\x* inkosi yeBhabhiloni yabuya yabulala zonke izikhulu zakoJuda.\x + 52.10.\x*
\v 7 Yasiphumputhekisa amehlo kaZedekhiya, yambopha ngamaketane ethusi amabili ukuze imuse eBhabhiloni.\x + 32.4. Hez. 12.13.\x*
\p
\v 8 AmaKhaladiya asetshisa indlu yenkosi lezindlu zabantu ngomlilo,\x + 21.10; 38.18,23; 52.12. 2 Kho. 25.8.\x* adilizela phansi imiduli yeJerusalema.
\v 9 Lensali yabantu eyayisele emzini, lalabo ababehlubukile,\x + 37.13.\x* ababehlubukile kuyo, lensali yabantu eyayisele, uNebuzaradani induna yabalindi yabathumba yabasa eBhabhiloni.
\v 10 Kodwa uNebuzaradani induna yabalindi watshiya elizweni lakoJuda ebantwini ababengabayanga\x + 40.7.\x* ababengelalutho, wabanika izivini lamasimu ngalolosuku.
\p
\v 11 UNebhukadirezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni waselaya ngesandla sikaNebuzaradani induna yabalindi ngoJeremiya esithi:
\v 12 Mthathe, umise amehlo akho kuye, ungamenzeli ulutho olubi, kodwa njengokukhuluma kwakhe kuwe wenze njalo ngaye.
\v 13 Ngakho bathuma oNebuzaradani induna yabalindi, loNebushazibani, uRabisarisi, loNerigali-Sharezi,\x + 37.13. Dan. 1.3. 2 Kho. 18.17.\x* uRabimagi, lazo zonke induna zenkosi yeBhabhiloni,\x + 37.13. Mat. 2.1. Dan. 2.2,12.\x*
\v 14 bathuma, bamthatha uJeremiya egumeni lentolongo,\x + 32.2; 38.28.\x* bamnikela\x + 40.1-5.\x* kuGedaliya,\x + 40.5-16; 41.1-4,6,9,10,16,18; 43.6. 2 Kho. 25.22-25.\x* indodana kaAhikhamu, indodana kaShafani,\x + 2 Kho. 22.12.\x* ukuze amkhuphe amuse endlini yakhe. Wasehlala phakathi kwabantu.\x + 37.12.\x*
\s UEbedimeleki uzakhululwa yiN\nd kosi\nd*
\p
\v 15 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kuJeremiya esavalelwe egumeni lentolongo,\x + 32.2; 38.28.\x*\x + 36.5.\x* lisithi:
\v 16 Hamba ukhulume kuEbedimeleki umEthiyophiya\x + 38.7.\x* uthi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Khangela, ngizakwehlisela amazwi ami kulumuzi ngokubi\x + Dan. 9.12.\x* kungeyisikho ngokuhle,\x + 14.11.\x* njalo azakuba phambi kwakho ngalolosuku.
\v 17 Kodwa ngizakophula ngalolosuku, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, njalo kawuyikunikelwa esandleni sabantu obesabayo.\x + 22.25.\x*
\v 18 Ngoba ngizakukhulula isibili, kawuyikuwa-ke ngenkemba, kodwa impilo yakho izakuba yimpango kuwe,\x + 21.9.\x* ngoba uthembele kimi,\x + 1 Lan. 5.20. Hlab. 25.2; 37.40.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.